    COMPOSER | ARRANGER | ORCHESTRATOR

    SCROLL

    Sean Brown is a composer, arranger, multi-instrumentalist, and conductor, renowned for his ability to evoke emotion and enhance storytelling through music. Studying at the European Academy of Fine Arts, he honed his craft and earned a graduate diploma in Film and Video Game Scoring. Armed with a deep understanding of composition and orchestration, Sean embarked on a career dedicated to bringing stories to life through music.

     

    He has showcased his talent on both the conductor's podium and through score writing, leading orchestras in both a leadership and production capacity. His work spans a diverse range of projects, from feature-length to short films, each underscored by his distinctive musical voice. Whether crafting sweeping melodies for epic adventures or subtle nuances for intimate dramas, Sean's compositions breathe life into every scene they accompany, leaving an indelible impression on audiences.

     

    With a boundless passion for his craft, Sean continues to captivate audiences and elevate cinematic storytelling through the power of music.
